item.author: senthil.thyagarajan@gmail.com (Senthil Thyagarajan)
item.description: My name is Senthil Thyagarajan. As a kid in school we used a stencil to draw the first map. Little did I know then that making maps would be my passion/profession. Here in Stencilled I would be working on projects to represent data in different forms of visualization and maps. This website is compiled using Hugo a static site generator and automatically deployed to AWS S3 using Wercker. All the code for this website is available freely on github.
